igcaption%3ESopnendu%20Mohanty%20worked%20at%20Citi%20for%20nearly%2020%20years%20and%20cofounded%20the%20Singapore%20FinTech%20Festival.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20back%20office%20roles%20in%20banks%20will%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest%20by%20AI.%3Cp%3EGFTN%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESopnendu%20Mohanty%2C%2053%2C%20is%20the%20group%20CEO%20of%20the%20global%20advisory%20and%20investment%20firm%20GFTN.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20worked%20at%20Citi%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%20and%20was%20the%20chief%20fintech%20officer%20at%20Singapore's%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMohanty%20said%20back%20office%20roles%20in%20banks%20will%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20working%20at%20the%20front%20and%20back%20offices%20of%20banks%20are%20going%20to%20have%20wildly%20different%20experiences%20with%20AI%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-veteran-ai-will-not-doom-junior-bankers-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESopnendu%20Mohanty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20group%20CEO%20of%20the%20global%20advisory%20and%20investment%20firm%20GFTN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMohanty%2C%2053%2C%20worked%20at%20Citi%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%20before%20joining%20Singapore's%20central%20bank%20as%20its%20first%20chief%20fintech%20officer%20in%202015.%20He's%20also%20a%20cofounder%20of%20the%20Singapore%20FinTech%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-how-artificial-intelligence-transforming-workflows-efficiencies-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edisruption%20posed%20by%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20depend%20on%20whether%20one%20works%20in%20a%20bank's%20front%2C%20middle%2C%20or%20back%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFront%20is%20all%20for%20the%20customer.%20The%20middle%20is%20all%20for%20the%20bank%2C%20and%20the%20back%20is%20just%20for%20processing%20all%20the%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohanty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242e25c3e-0ad9-4ba3-a9e8-b39927d306d9%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20will%20affect%20bank%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMohanty%20predicted%20that%20AI%20will%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20front-office%20jobs%2C%20including%20roles%20in%20investment%20banking%2C%20sales%20and%20trading%2C%20and%20corporate%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20also%20expects%20the%20middle%20office%2C%20which%20handles%20a%20bank's%20risk%20management%2C%20financial%20controls%2C%20and%20compliance%2C%20to%20benefit%20from%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20middle%20office%20is%20all%20about%20internal%20productivity.%20That%20definitely%20gets%20better%20because%20the%20AI%20tools%20will%20make%20them%20work%20better%20and%20more%20efficiently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20office%20roles%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest%20by%20AI%2C%20Mohtanty%20said.%20The%20back%20office%20spans%20functions%20such%20as%20information%20technology%2C%20human%20resources%2C%20and%20trade%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20office%20work%20may%20be%20reduced%20because%20you%20are%20automating%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20work%20in%20a%20much%20sharper%20way.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20impact%20on%20jobs%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20back%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20AI%20has%20sparked%20fears%20over%20its%20ability%20to%20eliminate%20jobs%20entirely.%20JPMorgan%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-jpmorgan-ai-extraordinary-consequences-transformative-internet-electricity-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJamie%20Dimon%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20his%20annual%20letter%20to%20shareholders%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20augment%20virtually%20every%20job%2C%20as%20well%20as%20impact%20our%20workforce%20composition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may